<p><strong>CHRONOLOGY:</strong> Hired through typical channels for notable performance in computer science. Assigned to I. T. Department at Site-15 in 1993. Promoted to Department Head in 1996 for notable performance in the containment of <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5241" target="_blank">SCP-5241</a>. Promoted to Site Director in 1999. Relocated to Site-87 and reassigned to the 'Pataphysics Department in 2002 per personal request. Promoted to Department Head in 2011 for notable developments in Theoretical 'Pataphysics.</p>
