<p>Howdy there. My name's Nathan aka <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/placeholder-mcd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6536693); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6536693&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610017131" alt="Placeholder McD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6536693)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/placeholder-mcd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6536693); return false;">Placeholder McD</a></span> aka LOGICIAN. I'm a 19-year-old Canadian guy studying Music Education (at the time of writing). I never really thought of myself as a writer, nor did I think writing was something I would enjoy, until I got into the SCP wiki; I had been sub-aware of the community and its basic concepts for several years, but only started really reading and interacting with the wiki in April/May 2020. Suddenly, I realized I could take all the weird, unrelated topics I'm unnaturally passionate / knowledgeable about and learn to present them in a way that people find interesting &#8212; which was probably my biggest weakness before I started working at it. Now I write stuff once in a while, and sometimes people like it, which is pretty cool.</p>
